### **Category 1: Repeated Object Construction / Test Data Setup**

**Severity: HIGH** — Extreme duplication in Order and OrderItem creation

**Examples:**
- **OrderProcessorTests.cs:**
  - Line 15-23: Order with C001/alice@example.com + single Widget (9.99m) with Qty 2
  - Line 38-47: Order with C002/bob@example.com + Widget + Gadget
  - Line 62-71: Order with C003/carol@example.com + single Widget (10.00m) with Qty 5
  - Line 86-91: Order with C004/dave@example.com + empty items
  - Line 106-114: Order with C005 + null email + Widget
