  - Line 254-262: Order with C004/dave@example.com + negative price Widget
  - Line 274-282: Order with C005/eve@example.com + zero quantity Widget

**Summary:** Nearly every test constructs Order and OrderItem objects from scratch with hardcoded values. The pattern is identical across all 13 methods. Multiple tests reuse the same customer IDs/emails (C001, C002, C003, etc.) and the same "Widget" product.

**Suggested Refactoring:**
